name: Restaurant penpen 73
address: kec tejakula, Desa, sembiran atas, Tejakula, Buleleng Regency, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: What an amazing experience. Beautiful view. A few monkeys  and service was top notch. One thing if you're a novice on a scooter, be careful, but they will drive your scooter down the steep part if u need them too.
review 2: North Bali’s greatest venue without question. Fantastic coffee, food and drinks and an enchanting view of the coastline from way up the hill. A bit of a wonderland!
review 3:
Last time i was coming with my friends woow the views so beautiful, the staffs. the food, healthy drink, and also the Atsmosphere. Next time for sure ww will be back again.
Cheers
review 4: Discover North Bali like never before, Penpen73 is the Balinese hotspot with stunning views, excellent food and service, The North is still pure, original and offended chiq, taste food in local culture setting Fin yards and grapes.
review 5: This is amazing place and food in north Bali i think..... 👍👍👍👍👍👍 I Love it...❤️❤️❤️
